sources.title: Le Bal (Musical, 1983) by Ettore Scola
sources.description:
Dance moves, music and fashion mark the passage of time inside a Paris dance hall, throughout fifty years of history.

Original title: Le bal

This film has no dialogue... only music

Director: Ettore Scola
Writers: Jean-Claude Penchenat, Ruggero Maccari, Furio Scarpelli
Stars: Étienne Guichard, Régis Bouquet, Francesco De Rosa
Genres: European Cinema compilation, History, Musical
